# $Header: /var/cvsroot/gentoo-x86/net-www/opera-static/ChangeLog,v 1.11 2003/05/28 23:18:09 agenkin Exp $

28 May 2003; Arcady Genkin <agenkin@gentoo.org> :
opera-static is removed in favor of the unified opera ebuild 
(net-www/opera).

*opera-static-6.1 (31 Oct 2002)

  31 Oct 2002; Arcady Genkin <agenkin@gentoo.org> opera-static-6.1.ebuild :
  
  Updated to 6.1.
  Now installing a symlink in /usr/bin.

*opera-static-6.03-r1 (21 Oct 2002)

  21 Oct 2002; Arcady Genkin <agenkin@gentoo.org> opera-static-6.03-r3.ebuild :
  
  Added x11-libs/lesstif to run-time dependencies.  This should allow using
  Netscape's Flash and Java plugins with Opera.  Thanks to Angel Ortiz
  <angelm75@optonline.net> for the research.

*opera-static-6.03 (20 August 2002)

  20 August 2002; Sascha Schwabbauer <cybersystem@gentoo.org> opera-static-6.03.ebuild :
  
  Bumped to version 6.03. SSL Security bug fixed.
  Ebuild by Tobias Eichert <tobias@databoogie.net>.

*opera-static-6.02 (20 August 2002)

  19 August 2002; Sascha Schwabbauer <cybersystem@gentoo.org> ChangeLog, opera-static-6.02.ebuild :

  Added -ppc to the keywords.

*opera-static-6.02 (4 Jul 2002)

  4 Jul 2002; Arcady Genkin <agenkin@thpoon.com> opera-static-6.02.ebuild:

  Version 6.02 is out.

*opera-static-6.0-r1 (4 Jul 2002)

  4 Jul 2002; Arcady Genkin <agenkin@thpoon.com> opera-static-6.0-r1.ebuild:

  Fixed the wrapper /opt/opera/share/bin/opera to not have $D in lots of
  places.

*opera-static-6.0 (20 May 2002)

  20 May 2002; Arcady Genkin <agenkin@thpoon.com> opera-static-6.0.ebuild:

  Initial version of the ebuild, adapted from the dynamically linked
  package.
